{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.1","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:1","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Aux mauvais riches<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-6: cf. Job 20:5, etc. Am 6:1-8; 5:11, 12. Mal 3:5; 4:1.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    A vous maintenant, riches! Pleurez et g\u00e9missez, \u00e0 cause des malheurs qui viendront sur vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.2","name":"Jacques 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.17","name":"Jacques 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.2","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:2","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Vos richesses sont pourries, et vos v\u00eatements sont rong\u00e9s par les teignes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.3","name":"Jacques 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.1","name":"Jacques 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.3","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:3","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Votre or et votre argent sont rouill\u00e9s; et leur rouille s\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8vera en t\u00e9moignage contre vous, et d\u00e9vorera vos chairs comme un feu. Vous avez amass\u00e9 des tr\u00e9sors dans les derniers jours!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.4","name":"Jacques 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.2","name":"Jacques 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.4","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:4","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Voici, le salaire des ouvriers qui ont moissonn\u00e9 vos champs, et dont vous les avez frustr\u00e9s, crie, et les cris des moissonneurs sont parvenus jusqu\u2019aux oreilles du Seigneur des arm\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.5","name":"Jacques 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.3","name":"Jacques 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.5","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:5","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Vous avez v\u00e9cu sur la terre dans les volupt\u00e9s et dans les d\u00e9lices, vous avez rassasi\u00e9 vos c\u0153urs au jour du carnage.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.6","name":"Jacques 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.4","name":"Jacques 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.6","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:6","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Vous avez condamn\u00e9, vous avez tu\u00e9 le juste, qui ne vous a pas r\u00e9sist\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.7","name":"Jacques 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.5","name":"Jacques 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.7","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:7","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.008,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Exhortations diverses: la patience, le serment, la pri\u00e8re, la conversion des p\u00e9cheurs<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 7-12: cf. H\u00e9 10:35-37; 6:12. 1 Pi 2:19-23; 4:12-19. Ja 1:12. Mt 5:33-37.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Soyez donc patients, fr\u00e8res jusqu\u2019\u00e0 l\u2019av\u00e8nement du Seigneur. Voici, le laboureur attend le pr\u00e9cieux fruit de la terre, prenant patience \u00e0 son \u00e9gard, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce qu\u2019il ait re\u00e7u les pluies de la premi\u00e8re et de l\u2019arri\u00e8re-saison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.8","name":"Jacques 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.6","name":"Jacques 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.8","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:8","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Vous aussi, soyez patients, affermissez vos c\u0153urs, car l\u2019av\u00e8nement du Seigneur est proche.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.9","name":"Jacques 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.7","name":"Jacques 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.9","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:9","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Ne vous plaignez pas les uns des autres, fr\u00e8res, afin que vous ne soyez pas jug\u00e9s: voici, le juge est \u00e0 la porte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.10","name":"Jacques 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.8","name":"Jacques 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.10","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:10","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Prenez, mes fr\u00e8res, pour mod\u00e8les de souffrance et de patience les proph\u00e8tes qui ont parl\u00e9 au nom du Seigneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.11","name":"Jacques 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.9","name":"Jacques 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.11","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:11","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Voici, nous disons bienheureux ceux qui ont souffert patiemment. Vous avez entendu parler de la patience de Job, et vous avez vu la fin que le Seigneur lui accorda, car le Seigneur est plein de mis\u00e9ricorde et de compassion.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.12","name":"Jacques 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.10","name":"Jacques 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.12","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:12","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Avant toutes choses, mes fr\u00e8res, ne jurez ni par le ciel, ni par la terre, ni par aucun autre serment. Mais que votre oui soit oui, et que votre non soit non, afin que vous ne tombiez pas sous le jugement.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.13","name":"Jacques 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.11","name":"Jacques 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.13","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:13","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-20: cf. (Ps 50:15. Mc 11:24.) (No 14:11-20. 1 R 17; 18.) Da 12:3.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Quelqu\u2019un parmi vous est-il dans la souffrance? Qu\u2019il prie. Quelqu\u2019un est-il dans la joie? Qu\u2019il chante des cantiques.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.14","name":"Jacques 5:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.12","name":"Jacques 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.14","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:14","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Quelqu\u2019un parmi vous est-il malade? Qu\u2019il appelle les anciens de l\u2019\u00c9glise, et que les anciens prient pour lui, en l\u2019oignant d\u2019huile au nom du Seigneur;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.15","name":"Jacques 5:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.13","name":"Jacques 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.15","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:15","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>la pri\u00e8re de la foi sauvera le malade, et le Seigneur le rel\u00e8vera; et s\u2019il a commis des p\u00e9ch\u00e9s, il lui sera pardonn\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.16","name":"Jacques 5:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.14","name":"Jacques 5:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.16","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:16","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Confessez donc vos p\u00e9ch\u00e9s les uns aux autres, et priez les uns pour les autres, afin que vous soyez gu\u00e9ris. La pri\u00e8re fervente du juste a une grande efficace.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.17","name":"Jacques 5:17","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.15","name":"Jacques 5:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.17","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:17","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>\u00c9lie \u00e9tait un homme de la m\u00eame nature que nous: il pria avec instance pour qu\u2019il ne pl\u00fbt point, et il ne tomba point de pluie sur la terre pendant trois ans et six mois.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.18","name":"Jacques 5:18","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.16","name":"Jacques 5:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.18","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:18","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Puis il pria de nouveau, et le ciel donna de la pluie, et la terre produisit son fruit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.19","name":"Jacques 5:19","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.17","name":"Jacques 5:17","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.19","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:19","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Mes fr\u00e8res, si quelqu\u2019un parmi vous s\u2019est \u00e9gar\u00e9 loin de la v\u00e9rit\u00e9, et qu\u2019un autre l\u2019y ram\u00e8ne,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.20","name":"Jacques 5:20","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.18","name":"Jacques 5:18","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.20","label":"","reference":"Jacques 5:20","prev_osis_id":"Jas.005.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.001.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.5.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>qu\u2019il sache que celui qui ram\u00e8nera un p\u00e9cheur de la voie o\u00f9 il s\u2019\u00e9tait \u00e9gar\u00e9 sauvera une \u00e2me de la mort et couvrira une multitude de p\u00e9ch\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.5","name":"Jacques 5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.1","name":"1 Pierre 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.19","name":"Jacques 5:19","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fba0db571.27573849');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fba0db571.27573849\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fba0db571.27573849","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fba0db571.27573849'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fba0db571.27573849\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}